    <title>《Flask Framework Cookbook》 学习笔记 - Flask 应用的配置</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2016/11/22/flaskcoolbook_1/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2016/11/22/flaskcoolbook_1/</id>
    <published>2016-11-22T02:39:00.052Z</published>
    <updated>2016-11-22T02:39:00.052Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>简单的Flask例子和安装就不讲了，大家去看官网的文档吧。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="1-基础的配置"><a href="#1-基础的配置" class="headerlink" title="1. 基础的配置"></a>1. 基础的配置</h2><p>想让我们的程序运行在调试模式下，可以这样配置：<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app = Flask(__name__)</div><div class="line">app.config[<span class="string">'DEBUG'</span>] = <span class="keyword">True</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>这个布尔值也可以通过Flask对象来设置：<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app.debug = <span class="keyword">True</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>一般情况下，我们都使用最开始那种方式去配置这个选项。</p>
<h2 id="2-常见的配置方式"><a href="#2-常见的配置方式" class="headerlink" title="2. 常见的配置方式"></a>2. 常见的配置方式</h2><ol>
<li><p>通过外部文件（*.cfg）等配置</p>
 <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app.config.from_pyfile(<span class="string">'myconfig.cfg'</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>通过一个对象来配置，一般这个对象是一个类，当然也可以是模块等等</p>
 <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app.config.from_object(<span class="string">'myapplication.default_settings'</span>)</div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果是要加载当前文件的配置，我们可以使用下面的方式 </span></div><div class="line">app.config.from_object(__name__) <span class="comment">#To load from same file</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>通过系统环境变量来配置</p>
 <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app.config.from_envvar(<span class="string">'PATH_TO_CONFIG_FILE'</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p> 在windows中可以这样设置PATH_TO_CONFIG_FILE这个变量：</p>
 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">set PATH_TO_CONFIG_FILE=c:\\config.cfg</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p> 在linux中可以这样设置：</p>
 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">export PATH_TO_CONFIG_FILE=c:\\config.cfg</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="3-类对象配置基本例子"><a href="#3-类对象配置基本例子" class="headerlink" title="3. 类对象配置基本例子"></a>3. 类对象配置基本例子</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">BaseConfig</span><span class="params">(object)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="string">'Base config class'</span></div><div class="line">    SECRET_KEY = <span class="string">'A random secret key'</span></div><div class="line">    DEBUG = <span class="keyword">True</span></div><div class="line">    TESTING = <span class="keyword">False</span></div><div class="line">    NEW_CONFIG_VARIABLE = <span class="string">'my value'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ProductionConfig</span><span class="params">(BaseConfig)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="string">'Production specific config'</span></div><div class="line">    DEBUG = <span class="keyword">False</span></div><div class="line">    SECRET_KEY = open(<span class="string">'/path/to/secret/file'</span>).read()</div><div class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">StagingConfig</span><span class="params">(BaseConfig)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="string">'Staging specific config'</span></div><div class="line">    DEBUG = <span class="keyword">True</span></div><div class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">DevelopmentConfig</span><span class="params">(BaseConfig)</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="string">'Development environment specific config'</span></div><div class="line">    DEBUG = <span class="keyword">True</span></div><div class="line">    TESTING = <span class="keyword">True</span></div><div class="line">    SECRET_KEY = <span class="string">'Another random secret key'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">## 可以这样使用</span></div><div class="line">app.config.from_object(<span class="string">'configuration.DevelopmentConfig‘)</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="4-静态文件"><a href="#4-静态文件" class="headerlink" title="4. 静态文件"></a>4. 静态文件</h2><p>一般默认情况下，会在应用同级目录下建立一个名为static的目录既可以。<br>*. 包模式<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">├── my_app</div><div class="line">│   ├── __init__.py</div><div class="line">│   ├── __init__.pyc</div><div class="line">│   ├── product</div><div class="line">│   │   ├── __init__.py</div><div class="line">│   │   ├── __init__.pyc</div><div class="line">│   │   ├── models.py</div><div class="line">│   │   ├── models.pyc</div><div class="line">│   │   ├── views.py</div><div class="line">│   │   └── views.pyc</div><div class="line">│   ├── static</div><div class="line">│   │   ├── css</div><div class="line">│   │   │   ├── bootstrap.min.css</div><div class="line">│   │   │   └── main.css</div><div class="line">│   │   └── js</div><div class="line">│   │       └── bootstrap.min.js</div><div class="line">│   └── templates</div><div class="line">│       ├── base.html</div><div class="line">│       ├── home.html</div><div class="line">│       └── product.html</div><div class="line">├── run.py</div><div class="line">└── setup.py</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>当然也可以通过配置进行指定：<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app = Flask(__name__, static_folder=<span class="string">'/path/to/static/folder'</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>如果要使用bootstrap.min.js，可以这样写：<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"/static/js/bootstrap.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>如果存在这样的配置：<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app = Flask(__name__, static_url_path=<span class="string">'/differentstatic'</span>,static_folder=<span class="string">'/path/to/static/folder'</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>那么可以这样使用：<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"/differentstatic/bootstrap.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong> 平常我们都不是这样用，下面方式才是最推荐使用的：</strong><br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"&#123;&#123; url_for('static', filename='js/bootstrap.min.js') &#125;&#125;"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="5-instance目录自动配置"><a href="#5-instance目录自动配置" class="headerlink" title="5. instance目录自动配置"></a>5. instance目录自动配置</h2><p>如果和应用同级下，存在instance这样一个目录，那么应用将会自动导入instance目录下的配置信息。<br>可以在配置文件中指定这个目录的地址：<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app = Flask(__name__, instance_path=<span class="string">'/absolute/path/to/instance/folder'</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong> 为了加载这个目录下的配置，我们需要设置instance_relative_config </strong><br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app = Flask(__name__, instance_relative_config=<span class="keyword">True</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong> 通过这样读取配置 </strong><br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app.config.from_pyfile(<span class="string">'config.cfg'</span>, silent=<span class="keyword">True</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
    
